Author: this_isnt_me_bed
Text: This is me in a nutshell. I doubt I will ever get there because I'm a fat fuck who cant commit to anything but I'll die trying.

Author: vfgoiugkjgdslk
Text: It sucks and I feel like I'm on the verge of death but getting to a healthy weight is as equally terrifying as dying to me. I felt bad when I was a normal weight but back then I don't think my health problems were so severe. I'm not trying to say this in an "im suffering more" kind of way but in like a "I know your ED idolizes this because so did mine but it legitimately fucking sucks and I want better for you than what I'm experiencing" kind of way  Please be kind to yourself whenever possible
